high_descs: turn to the right and walk to the fridge at the end of the room, then turn right and walk to the end of the kitchen island on your right, and turn right to face it
grab the knife off of the kitchen island counter top
turn around and walk to the sink which is almost immediately behind you to begin with
cut up the tomato in to slices inside of the sink please
turn around to back up a bit, then turn back around to face the sink again
place the knife down in the cabinet to the left of the sink, which is below the sink
look up at the kitchen sink so you can see the tomato slices better
grab a tomato slice out of the inside of the kitchen sink
turn right and walk over to the kitchen stove, then look up to face the microwave better
place the tomato slice inside of the microwave to begin cooking it, begin cooking it, then take it out when it is done
turn around and walk to the kitchen island counter just ahead on your left
place the tomato slice down on the counter in front of the other tomato
anns.task_desc: place a cooked tomato slice down on the kitchen island counter

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right after the green table ends on the right, go forward, turn right near the end of the green table on the right, go toward to the table.
Take the large knife from the table.
Turn around, go forward to the sink.
Cut the tomato in the sink into slices.
Move backwards from the sink then face the sink.
Put the knife on the plate in the bottom left cabinet under the sink.
Move forward to the sink.
Take a slice of tomato from the sink.
Turn right, move forward to the oven.
Cook the slice of tomato in the microwave above the oven, then take the tomato out.
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the green table.
Put the tomato between the apple and the table edge on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato on a table.

high_descs: TUrn right and walk across the room then turn right and cross the room and turn left to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the kitchen table.
Turn around and walk forward to face the sink.
Cut the tomato in the sink into slices.
Step back and look down to face the cabinet under the sink.
Place the knife in the left side cabinet under the sink.
Step forward to face the tomato in the sink.
Pick up a slice of the tomato in the sink.
Turn to the right and walk forward to face the microwave above the stove.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and cross half the room and then turn left to face the kitchen table.
Place the tomato slice on the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: To cut plus heat a slice of tomato as well as put it on the kitchen table.

high_descs: walk to the right, turn right near the fridge, walk straight and face the knife on the green table.
Pick up the knife on top of the table next to the pan.
turn around and go to the sink.
cut the stem of the tomato in the sink.
Bring the knife to the cabinet underneath the sink.
Open the door of the cabinet, put it inside and close the door.
Look back up to the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the sink.
Go slightly to the right towards the stove. Look up to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put it in, heat the tomato for a few seconds, pick it up and close the microwave.
Turn around and go to the green table again. Face the pan on top of the table.
Put the slice of tomato in front of the apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of heated tomato in front of the apple on the green table.

high_descs: Turn right and go around the end of the island to end by the stove.
Pick up the knife from the island.
Turn around and move to the sink.
Slice the tomato that's in the sink.
Move a few inches to the left.
Open the left cabinet under the sink and put the knife on the plate.
Move a few steps closer to the sink.
Pick up a tomato slice from the sink.
Turn to the right and go to the microwave above the stove.
Cook the tomato in the microwave for a few seconds.
Turn around and move to the island on your left.
Set the tomato slice on the island in front of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked tomato slice on the island in front of the apple.

high_descs: Turn right, turn right and walk to the green-topped table, turn right to face the table.
Pick up yellow-handled knife from the table.
Turn left, turn left again, to face the sink.
Cut a slice from the tomato in the sink.
Turn completely around counter-clockwise, to face the sink again.
Open the left hand door of the cabinet below the sink and put the knife in it.
Walk toward the sink and back up from it a little.
Pick up the tomato slice from the sink.
Turn to the right, turn right, then turn left to face the stove.
Put the slice of tomato in the microwave about the stove and turn on the microwave.
Take the tomato from the microwave, turn right and walk to the table.
Put the tomato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a tomato slice on the table.
